### Notice & Purpose
This codebase is a designated portfolio piece, developer showcase, and project application sample created for clients by **Jelvan Ricolcol**. It is designed to illustrate excellence in client-side zero-knowledge security, elegant high-contrast visual design, local-first workflows, and performance optimization on standard Node.js server environments.
